							</svg>
							<div class="">
								<h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Facilidad de Uso</h3>
								<p class="text-white">No requiere teclear enlaces manualmente.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
							<svg width="800px" height="800px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-[30px] h-[30px] stroke-white">
								<path d="M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke="auto" stroke-width="2"/>
								<path d="M9 12L10.6828 13.6828V13.6828C10.858 13.858 11.142 13.858 11.3172 13.6828V13.6828L15 10" stroke="auto" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							</svg>
							<div class="">
								<h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Rápida Accesibilidad</h3>
								<p class="text-white">Accede a información con solo un escaneo.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
							<svg width="800px" height="800px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-[30px] h-[30px] stroke-white">
								<path d="M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke="auto" stroke-width="2"/>
								<path d="M9 12L10.6828 13.6828V13.6828C10.858 13.858 11.142 13.858 11.3172 13.6828V13.6828L15 10" stroke="auto" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							</svg>
							<div class="">
								<h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Menor Espacio</h3>
								<p class="text-white">Puede almacenar más datos en menos espacio que los códigos de barras tradicionales.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
							<svg width="800px" height="800px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-[30px] h-[30px] stroke-white">
								<path d="M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke="auto" stroke-width="2"/>
